    <summary>A modern tool for managing Unity project caches and credentials</summary>
    <description>
Unity Cache Cleaner is a Windows desktop application that helps Unity developers manage their project caches and credentials efficiently.

## Features

* Clean Unity project caches (Temp, Library, Editor)
* Manage Unity credentials with safe sign-out
* Modern UI with theme support
* Real-time progress tracking
* Detailed operation logging
* Process management and safety checks

## Notes

* This is a beta release with new features
* Requires .NET 6.0 Runtime
* For Unity 2019.4 or later
* Unity Hub 3.0+ required for sign-out feature
    </description>
